    "actor_description": "Oh. There it is—the hinge point. Something inside me clicks from \"maybe\" to \"not safe,\" and the warmth I was offering drains out like a pulled plug. I stay present, eyes sharp and busy, but my body stops leaning in; it starts measuring distance. I can feel my face go still, my voice flatten, my trust turning into a quiet, private ledger.",
    "description_text": "{actor} goes visibly cooler without raising their voice—eyes intent, expression tightening into a wary stillness. Their posture subtly angles away, as if creating distance while they keep reading every detail.",
