            "failure_message": "Requires an alert, engaged threat appraisal where suspicion clears its gate (arousal >= 0, engagement high) and affiliation turns negative (warmth withdraws). Excludes rage/hatred so it reads as cold realization, and caps panic/freeze so it doesn’t collide with overwhelm or immobility. Triggers only on a suspicion spike, threat jump, or sharp affiliation drop to prevent spam."
